---
// Section 7: Final CTA - primary conversion section
---
<section id="contact" class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-brand-ink text-white overflow-hidden">
  <div
    class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full opacity-[0.18]"
    style="background: radial-gradient(circle, #EC4899 0%, transparent 60%);"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full opacity-[0.18]"
    style="background: radial-gradient(circle, #22D3EE 0%, transparent 60%);"
  >
  </div>
  <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <span class="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.2em] gradient-text uppercase">Get started</span>
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl font-medium mt-4 mb-6 leading-tight">
      まずは、お問い合わせから。
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 text-base leading-loose mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      案件内容をお伺いして、お見積もりをお送りします。<br class="hidden md:inline" />
      現在の課題、対応可能エリアのご確認など、お気軽にご相談ください。
    </p>
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
      
        href="mailto:contact@praeternum.com"
        class="cta-btn inline-block text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-md text-sm font-medium w-full md:w-auto tracking-wide"
      >
        お問い合わせフォームへ
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-8 max-w-xs mx-auto">
      <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-white/15"></div>
      <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 tracking-wider">or</span>
      <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-white/15"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">LINEでのご相談も承ります</p>
      
        href="https://lin.ee/8sYxwhd"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#06C755] hover:bg-[#05B34A] transition px-8 py-3 rounded-md text-sm font-medium text-white"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19.365 9.863c.349 0 .63.285.63.631 0 .345-.281.63-.63.63H17.61v1.125h1.755c.349 0 .63.283.63.63 0 .344-.281.629-.63.629h-2.386c-.345 0-.627-.285-.627-.629V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63h2.386c.346 0 .627.285.627.63 0 .349-.281.63-.63.63H17.61v1.125h1.755zm-3.855 3.016c0 .27-.174.51-.432.596-.064.021-.133.031-.199.031-.211 0-.391-.09-.51-.25l-2.443-3.317v2.94c0 .344-.279.629-.631.629-.346 0-.626-.285-.626-.629V8.108c0-.27.173-.51.43-.595.06-.023.136-.033.194-.033.195 0 .375.104.495.254l2.462 3.33V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63.345 0 .63.285.63.63v4.771zm-5.741 0c0 .344-.282.629-.631.629-.345 0-.627-.285-.627-.629V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63.346 0 .628.285.628.63v4.771zm-2.466.629H4.917c-.345 0-.63-.285-.63-.629V8.108c0-.345.285-.63.63-.63.348 0 .63.285.63.63v4.141h1.756c.348 0 .629.283.629.63 0 .344-.282.629-.629.629M24 10.314C24 4.943 18.615.572 12 .572S0 4.943 0 10.314c0 4.811 4.27 8.842 10.035 9.608.391.082.923.258 1.058.59.12.301.079.766.038 1.08l-.164 1.02c-.045.301-.24 1.186 1.049.645 1.291-.539 6.916-4.078 9.436-6.975C23.176 14.393 24 12.458 24 10.314"/></svg>
        友だち追加
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-10">
      営業時間：平日 9:00-18:00 / 通常、当日〜翌営業日までにご返信いたします。
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
